trans-unit.source: Describes the versions of the .NET Framework that an application can run on.
trans-unit.target: Beskriver versionerna av .NET Framework som ett program kan köras på.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.CompatibleFramework"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.CompatibleFramework"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Represents the profile of the corresponding .NET Framework.
A profile is a subset of the full .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: En profil är en delmängd av fullständig .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: For example, the [!INCLUDE[net_client_v35_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v35-long-md.md)] is a subset of the [!INCLUDE[net_v35SP1_long](~/add/includes/net-v35sp1-long-md.md)], and the [!INCLUDE[net_client_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v40-long-md.md)] is a subset of the [!INCLUDE[net_v45](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den [!INCLUDE[net_client_v35_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v35-long-md.md)] är en delmängd av den [!INCLUDE[net_v35SP1_long](~/add/includes/net-v35sp1-long-md.md)], och [!INCLUDE[net_client_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v40-long-md.md)] är en delmängd av den [!INCLUDE[net_v45](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [.NET Framework Client Profile](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [.NET Framework Client Profile](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> object that represents the profile of the.NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>objekt som representerar profilen för.NET Framework.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the supported runtime for the framework.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger stöds runtime för ramen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> object that represents a runtime version of the corresponding .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>objekt som representerar en körningsversion av motsvarande .NET Framework.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the version of the framework.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger versionen av framework.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> object that represents the version of a .NET Framework.
Gets or sets the XML version for the framework.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger XML-version för ramen.

trans-unit.source: An array of XML elements that represents the profile of the.NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: En matris med XML-element som representerar profilen för.NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the XML supported runtime for the framework.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger XML stöds runtime för ramen.

trans-unit.source: An array of XML elements that represents the runtime version of the corresponding .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: En matris med XML-element som representerar körningsversion av motsvarande .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the version of the framework.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger versionen av framework.

trans-unit.source: An array of XML elements that represents the version of a .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: En matris med XML-element som representerar versionen av en .NET Framework.
